---
description: "Formatting commands"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Format Dart: `dart format --line-length 120 <files>`.
- Format Python: `black --line-length 120 --skip-string-normalization <files>`.
- Format C/C++: `clang-format -i <files>`.
- Do not manually format generated Dart files (`*.gen.dart`, `*.g.dart`).
- See AGENTS.md for full rules.
